Zen5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> AM5?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"Zen4要轉socket，DDR5"},{"pid":"befdf85b3b71cc6a4eacfb0c29ad1122bff182b3","tid":2378021,"uid":56989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b11fec3b58b333316575a35c919be6badb744bd1","tid":2378021,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b1f65ba0e40901e02911a486a3fb2de1437b78","tid":2378021,"uid":56989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"Zen 4 Zen5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> AM5?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"Zen4要轉socket，DDR5"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續用AM4先"},{"pid":"bfdeca5d84e6cd548c618a4ad4666673948a7f6f","tid":2378021,"uid":182822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"tsm amd gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122c3867ab7cf744dff39a635842006cdccb05ef","tid":2378021,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"空氣cpu"},{"pid":"b2d14846acfc7106365b312d8c0b33c2248fd178","tid":2378021,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf2b386c06b3cc674465dee2b6a1e51c15a234e","tid":2378021,"uid":1518,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"Intel：2023先有7nm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"煙條好似已經同台積電傾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fcc3997e7bc0aa92843b51c812e7bf428deba2","tid":2378021,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b5a5f42579a72252d2c4b119b38e892d1c3204","tid":2378021,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2021/01/source/23014718381200285188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2021%2F01%2Fsource%2F23014718381200285188.jpg&h=2907c24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於兩代額產品的核心數量一直保持不變，目前 Ryzen Mobile 版最多為 8 核心、Ryzen Desktop 版最多為 16 核心、HEDT 及伺服器最多為 64 核心，那麼是否會成為事實上的極限？<br />\n <br />\n對此，「蘇媽」表示：「未來肯定會有更多的核心數量，我不會說這就是極限，伺服器 / HEDT 平台或許會增加到 96 核心、Desktop 版最多或增加到 32 核心、Mobile 版則會增加到 12~16 核心，並會隨著我們對系統其他部分的擴展而出現。」<br />\n <br />\n至於發佈時間，「蘇媽」透露 Zen 4 預計會在 2021年底的某個時候出現，請大家耐心期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2021/01/source/2302070626395314262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2021%2F01%2Fsource%2F2302070626395314262.jpg&h=ea4207ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"如果Intel 新CEO全力谷ARM 嘅CPU，AMD就含得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9496b9ace14bddd9991b5d01d42c2fe72f6ba034","tid":2378021,"uid":219117,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25fcc3997e7bc0aa92843b51c812e7bf428deba2","tid":2378021,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b5a5f42579a72252d2c4b119b38e892d1c3204","tid":2378021,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2021/01/source/23014718381200285188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2021%2F01%2Fsource%2F23014718381200285188.jpg&h=2907c24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於兩代額產品的核心數量一直保持不變，目前 Ryzen Mo